data.description: Amazing location and views!  In this gated community where homes rarely go on the market, this 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath open floor plan comes with a huge loft (second family room), wet bar and attached deck to view the amazing unobstructed sunrise and open valley views. The home has an expansive kitchen with a pantry, island and kitchen nook, formal dining room along with a large front yard, two private side patios and an attached 2-car garage all located on a cul-de-sac street along with your very own community dog park! All three bedrooms are located on the upper level with two full bathrooms. Situated in the heart of Encinitas, minutes from restaurants, shopping and more.
